How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzes reviews to verify trustworthiness.

Sels
4.0 out of 5 stars Decent quality, my students loved them
Reviewed in the United States on November 28, 2021
Color: 21 PcsVerified Purchase
I'm not really into these toys, but kids love em. I bought them to give to my Sped students.

As some other reviews said, yes, there are a few imperfections. Of the 21 pieces I received, 5 were a little messy on the edges and one of those had a tiiiny hole where the silicone didn't fuse together fully. But it wasn't at all hard to clean them up, i just pulled off the excess.

I also don't think they "pop" as well as other popper toys do. One side popped well ("soo satisfying!" Says my student) but the other would get stuck and you'd have to push it twice or a little harder to make it stay down.

Other than that, I thought they were a good gift. It's a good price for the amount you get, in my opinion. Most importantly, my students LOVED them and right away stuck them on their belt loops, lunchboxes, backpacks, necklaces...they absolutely loved them!! So that makes me happy
